{"tid":411722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[點解而家既人可以係咁]從來未試過 帶阿婆(85+)出街可以冇人讓位比佢坐","createTime":"2017-09-24T05:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T12:04:00.000Z","uid":49388,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f0986085a09246d15c1c140965ff4612a33c5b2","tid":411722,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:21:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WoYuenLong/posts/1362189073893724\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWoYuenLong%2Fposts%2F1362189073893724&d=eBMiSzoz1NJ4r%2F85aWCwp4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=591c454b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WoYuenLong/posts/1362189073893724</a><br />\n20170923 22:xx 一往上水77k上<br />\n從來未試過 帶阿婆(85+)出街可以冇人讓位比佢坐<br />\n果時同佢上車 叫佢入去搵位坐我入錢<br />\n心諗平時都有好心人會讓位比佢坐<br />\n點知呢四個坐緊關愛座既人喺度玩手機當睇唔到<br />\n後面幾個位既見到都唔讓位(如圖藍圈人仕)<br />\n佢行到入面巴士後輪個度先有位坐(如圖紅色指住果度)<br />\n我唔明點解而家既人可以係咁<br />\n成日話人坐關愛座係廢青 你班八十前坐關愛座點解唔係廢中<br />\n都算 諗住窄都企阿婆隔離睇佢有咩需要即刻幫到<br />\n出面有個阿姐行入黎怒睥我 好似想叫我死開咁<br />\n原來想開開心心同下阿婆出街 都攪到憤怒收場<br />\n今次影唔到你地班人個樣 下次一定要比全世界都知道你地個衰樣<br />\n希望大家關注事件 同關心身邊有需要既人<br />\n利申 : 18歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/131931_d7866c33d79852c39b097073ae5000ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F131931_d7866c33d79852c39b097073ae5000ce.jpg&h=36baca52&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37209af90f6ac7dac39c028acb033d21f5a62202","tid":411722,"uid":53122,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:25:35.000Z","msg":"你明知阿婆咁多需要<br />\n<br />\n你唔call 架uber 載佢<br />\n<br />\n你on9 ?"},{"pid":"4646342fc0425e82d6aa7cb5263ac351b3cd8c0c","tid":411722,"uid":27354,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:30:32.000Z","msg":"咁撚孝順就咪撚帶佢坐巴士啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e3e845b5936cfe4c1b994b5f69519336fd2bfc","tid":411722,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:33:40.000Z","msg":"呢個case 我覺得咁<br />\n本身係有位其實冇乜好嘈<br />\n唯一前面座關愛坐個哥仔有d on居<br />\n有其他位緊係坐其他位先啦<br />\n萬一架車full左而又有幾個老人家/大肚婆上車<br />\n你咪變左侷起身冇位座"},{"pid":"701e909dcbc3aefec912503f938a4a9860ecfdd1","tid":411722,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:35:40.000Z","msg":"越多批鬥文越唔會讓座"},{"pid":"460985543b362478d65185800f01592b0bcc3c7d","tid":411722,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:35:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個case 我覺得咁<br />\n本身係有位其實冇乜好嘈<br />\n唯一前面座關愛坐個哥仔有d on居<br />\n有其他位緊係坐其他位先啦<br />\n萬一架車full左而又有幾個老人家/大肚婆上車<br />\n你咪變左侷起身冇位座</blockquote><br />\n你都on9<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一坐上去就扮訓啦梗係"},{"pid":"19b1d86559057c69a674badff99afcfc3a9268d3","tid":411722,"uid":38194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:23:37.000Z","msg":"講真點解一定要讓你？"},{"pid":"5751c201fe539321ba0454c3683f6ee214c10b7d","tid":411722,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:49:13.000Z","msg":"會唔會你呀婆乞人憎?<br />\n平時我呀婆好多人讓，但佢唔坐。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記得呢個係連登答法。"},{"pid":"24522ccd5ddec471d82c309b10c303f2190a2b12","tid":411722,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:58:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4dc875f2eed6a0837f8dfe8ffd40bbe0ca38fbc2","tid":411722,"uid":27509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:01:56.000Z","msg":"架巴士仲有位都要人讓座？"},{"pid":"8502c6ec6dc402332ce5b69abf1f2f8cc06f018b","tid":411722,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:04:00.000Z","msg":"唔明點解唔買車 叫的士,Uber, gogo van要坐巴士呢?"}]}